            <p><a class="" target="" href="/web/20180712205446/https://www.guideline.gov/summaries/summary/51294/clinical-practice-guideline-on-systemic-lupus-erythematosus">Clinical practice guideline on systemic lupus erythematosus.</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="list-item-small">
        <ul class="item-meta">
            <li> NGC:011385</li>
            <li>2018 Mar</li>
        </ul>
       
            <p><a class="" target="" href="/web/20180712205446/https://www.guideline.gov/summaries/summary/51326/vadod-clinical-practice-guideline-for-the-management-of-pregnancy">VA/DoD clinical practice guideline for the management of pregnancy.</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="list-item-small">
        <ul class="item-meta">
            <li> NGC:011376</li>
            <li>2018 Feb</li>
        </ul>
       
